import * as React from 'react';
import { Card } from '@material-ui/core';
import { Button } from '@material-ui/core';

import arcade from '../images/arcade.png'

const Immagini = () => {
        return (
            <>  
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> {arcade} </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 2 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 3 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 4 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 5 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 6 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid",float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 7 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 8 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid",float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 9 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 10 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid",float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 11 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 12 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 13 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"left"}} > <Button> Img 14 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid",float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 15 </Button>
            </Card>
            <Card style={{backgroundColor:"grey", border: "5px", borderColor:"black", borderStyle:"solid", float:"right"}} > <Button> Img 16 </Button>
            </Card>
            </>
        );
}
 
export default Immagini;
